graph TD
    subgraph UI_Layer
        Web[Web App]
        Mobile[Mobile App]
    end

    subgraph Command_Side_Write
        API_W[Command API]
        Domain[Domain Logic/Validation]
        DB_W[(Write DB - Normalized)]
    end

    subgraph Query_Side_Read
        API_R[Query API]
        Cache[Redis/Elasticsearch]
        DB_R[(Read DB - De-normalized)]
    end

    Web --> API_W
    Mobile --> API_W
    API_W --> Domain
    Domain --> DB_W

    DB_W -- Async Sync/Events --> DB_R
    DB_R --> Cache

    Web --> API_R
    Mobile --> API_R
    API_R --> Cache
